  "name": "Phantom Pain",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Illusory pain wracks the target, dealing 2d4 mental damage and [[/r (@item.level)d4[persistent,mental]]] damage. The target must attempt a Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes full initial damage but no persistent damage, and the spell ends immediately.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes full initial and persistent damage, and the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1}. If the target recovers from being Sickened, the persistent damage ends and the spell ends.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d4 and the persistent damage by 1d4.</p>"
    },
